Usage: fixVia [-help] [-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}] {-short | -minCut | -minStep | -cutSpacing }

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}              # Specifies violation fixing area
                                 # (box, optional)
-cutSpacing                      # Fix cut spacing by trimming cuts
                                 # (bool, required)
-minCut                          # Fix mincut vias (bool, required)
-minStep                         # Fix minstep vias (bool, required)
-short                           # Fix short vias (bool, required)